{"tid":2266490,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"翻工之後反而唔捨得用錢","createTime":"2020-11-01T10:56:33.000Z","updateTime":"2020-11-01T11:22:04.000Z","uid":367093,"like":2,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":3,"replies":[{"pid":"245b13bab313dfb8a7b73e5ed934af2356ace648","tid":2266490,"uid":367093,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-01T10:56:33.000Z","msg":"原本以為翻工之後 有多啲錢會買多啲嘢 開心下<br />\n點知依家望到啲嘢個價錢<br />\n會諗呢個係我幾多幾多個鐘嘅人工<br />\n之後即刻唔想買<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n到依家一件衫都冇買過<br />\n連原本諗住買新銀包 都係用贈品<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"879bd17669c7f99a73c7dea2ee4059c3d7779217","tid":2266490,"uid":201414,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-01T10:58:29.000Z","msg":"去富士洗下樓 你就會感受到洗錢嘅樂趣<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6f90b0646f347c5afdac9d1cae1f92f2acb2bd29","tid":2266490,"uid":233267,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-01T11:22:04.000Z","msg":"我都係 明白到返工辛苦 錢得來不易"}]}